couple of weeks 
it will be a test case we will follow up the project depending 
on the success and response he said 
according to a un report on afghanistan most afghans are 
malnourished the average life expectancy is 41 years and the 
infant mortality rate is 200 per 1000 children 
if the project is successful it will be good news dewan 
said 
